## Architecture

Hexagonal architecture (Ports & Adapters):
- cmd/ — entrypoint only
- internal/domain/ — pure business logic, no framework imports
- internal/infrastructure/ — adapters: DB, cache, messaging, HTTP clients
- internal/presentation/ — inbound adapters: HTTP handlers
- internal/app/ — application services, orchestration

## Non-Negotiable Standards

- HTTP responses: RFC 7807 error format only — never raw error strings
- Logging: structured JSON via slog — never fmt.Println or log.Printf
- Tracing: W3C traceparent propagated on all inbound and outbound HTTP calls
- Health: /health /ready /live must always return correct status
- No global state — all dependencies injected via constructors
- Fail fast on misconfiguration — validate all env vars at startup
- Tests: table-driven pattern only

